  Locus:
    Page: 183
    Verse: 11
Tags:
  - Giving
---
The soul lives forever by giving, not receiving. This is the grand
paradox. You get most by giving most. Conversely, by receiving much you
impoverish yourself. By selfish accumulation you become bankrupt.
